    "The infinitesimal change in S is (5.12)The delta-function transforms with the opposite sign 39 giving [αK, δ(S)] = 2αδ(S).",
    "38 We have been able to show that this result generalises to states that have been acted on by the ∂ X j n and Ψ A,j r DDF operators of (3.7), but have not verified the radial symmetry when there are insertions containing ∂X j n. We expect the result to fully generalise and hope to return to this elsewhere.",
